divs: Sighting DetailsI was in Seattle last year. Vacationing just taking some pictures,took this shot of the harbor of a passenger ship. Now I did not see anything out of the usual. Were we got back I looked at all the pictures, saw these lights and though I might have something. Well I let it go till now I went though them again and blew this one way up. I would like for you to take a look at the left hand corner and see if you see what looks like a ufo? I did not mean to let this go for so long,but life gets in the way. Please let me know what you think. This picture has not in anyway been touched up. {pid}
